ls, double glazed window, single bowl, single drainer, fitted wall units, fitted base units, space for washing machine \r", "\r", "Conservatory\r", "7'01 x 15'07", "Laminated flooring, double glazed doors to garden, single glazed window, power points\r", "\r", "Landing\r", "Laminated flooring\r", "\r", "Bedroom One\r", "16'02 x 8'10 to wardrobes", "Laminated flooring, power points, double glazed bay window, gas radiator, built in wardrobes\r", "\r", "Bedroom Two\r", "11'11 x 10'05", "Laminated flooring, power points, gas radiator, double glazed window, sunken spot lights\r", "\r", "Bedroom Three\r", "8'05 x 6'04", "Laminated flooring, power points, gas radiator, double glazed box window\r", "\r", "Bathroom\r", "8'07 x 5'10", "Laminated flooring, gas radiator, tiled walls, low level flush toilet, hand basin, vanity unit, panelled bath with mixer tap and shower attachment, airing cupboard, double glazed window, sunken spot lights \r", "\r", "Garden\r", "54'03 x 17'07", "Decking area, laid to lawn, fences to side and rear, shed\r", "\r"]}
{"url": "http://www.rightmove.co.uk/property-for-sale/property-70986854.html", "description": ["\r\n        ", " ", " A Character Filled Two Bedroom House just off Southbury Road, providing easy access to the ever lively Enfield Town shopping parade. Ideally located within a short walk to Enfield Town BR station & Bush Hill Park BR Station (getting you into central London within 35 minutes), whilst benefitting from being situated in the heart of a thriving community, near local shops, cafes, supermarkets and within close proximity to Good and Higher Rated Ofsted Schools which families will appreciate. Southbury Leisure centre and Cineworld cinema are only a 5 minutes' walk away.", "\u00a0", " ", " ", " Presented over two floors this rare Victorian End of Terrace house comprises a picturesque living area with double glazing, laminated flooring and opens up into the dining area. Where there is another fireplace, adding more character to this stunning property. The kitchen is modern yet fits in line with the theme of the house, matching wall and base cabinets finished with a remarkable wooden work top and textured splash back tiles. Beyond the kitchen you will take advantage of a utility/conservatory area which leads to the delightful rear garden.", " The first floor consists of two generously sized bedrooms one being the master, with original wood flooring and neutrally painted walls. Also on this floor you will appreciate a spacious four piece family bathroom, with a large corner bath tub, a separate shower cubical and matching WC & wash basin.", "\u00a0", " ", " Being an End of terrace, this property benefits from having side access into the rear garden, which is well kept.", "This beautiful home is rare to the lettings market and will go fast, call now to arrange a viewing. \u00a0"]}
